build a go-kart,

13:05.267 --> 13:07.433
which would have been
hard enough.

13:07.433 --> 13:09.367
Instead, I would have to try
and convince

13:09.367 --> 13:11.100
to former love of my life

13:11.100 --> 13:13.267
to move in with a jerk.

13:13.267 --> 13:15.400
[sighs]

13:15.400 --> 13:18.867
Wow, I was just thinking
about Joe in there.

13:18.867 --> 13:20.433
He's fantastic.

13:20.433 --> 13:21.867
What a--what a great guy.

13:21.867 --> 13:23.833
Yeah, he is great.
I-I really like him.

13:23.833 --> 13:25.133
- Yeah. You do, huh?
- Yeah.

13:25.133 --> 13:26.433
