13:56.200 --> 13:58.700
For that, I would need to
convince my betrayer.

13:58.700 --> 14:01.900
You guys are basically like my
favorite couple I've ever seen.

14:01.900 --> 14:03.067
I like her, man.

14:03.067 --> 14:04.533
Ever since
I started dating her,

14:04.533 --> 14:06.867
whenever I get a little
something on the side,

14:06.867 --> 14:09.067
I feel pretty bad about it.

14:09.067 --> 14:11.833
Did you say that you have
already cheated on Suzanne?

14:11.833 --> 14:14.333
Yeah, but I'm gonna
try not to.

14:14.333 --> 14:16.067
Yeah, yeah.
No, that would be great.

14:16.067 --> 14:18.667
(Forrest voice-over)
Joe did not strike me
as a family man,

14:18.667 --> 14:20.500
but I could not give up.

14:20.500 --> 14:22.833
You should ask her
to move in with you.

14:22.833 --> 14:25.133
Mm, I gotta tell you.

14:25.133 --> 14:28.200
I like to throw
freaky parties, you know?

14:28.200 --> 14:30.300
Like, good-looking women
