14:49.067 --> 14:50.367
I had that, you know.

14:50.367 --> 14:52.967
You could really
literally just

14:52.967 --> 14:56.233
walk down there
and go get it.

14:56.233 --> 14:58.967
Cheers, man.

14:58.967 --> 15:00.867
Who's ready to play?

15:00.867 --> 15:03.067
(Forrest voice-over)
I had tried my best
to make a wish come true,

15:03.067 --> 15:06.300
but I doubted that a shallow man
like Joe Dale Jr.

15:06.300 --> 15:08.367
would make this sort of
commitment to a woman

15:08.367 --> 15:10.300
no matter how great she is.

15:10.300 --> 15:13.100
[dramatic music]

