15:19.867 --> 15:21.133
I got it. I got it. Oh!

15:21.133 --> 15:22.267
- Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa.
- I got it.

15:22.267 --> 15:23.800
- You got it?
- Yeah, I got it.

15:23.800 --> 15:25.800
(Forrest voice-over)
I had fulfilled my son's wish,

15:25.800 --> 15:28.733
and aside from
the truly awful feelings

15:28.733 --> 15:30.633
associated with
delivering my family

15:30.633 --> 15:33.300
into the hands of
a habitually unfaithful fraud,

15:33.300 --> 15:35.933
I can report that
it was satisfying

15:35.933 --> 15:38.467
to see the wish recipient
so happy.

15:38.467 --> 15:40.700
Dad.
