15:40.700 --> 15:42.767
Suzanne invited me to stay

15:42.767 --> 15:45.700
in one of Joe Dale Jr.'s
guesthouses.

15:45.700 --> 15:47.967
Sleeping on the floor
in your office

15:47.967 --> 15:50.167
