16:00.433 --> 16:03.200
(Forrest voice-over)
The idea that making
someone else's wish come true

16:03.200 --> 16:05.367
would involve any sacrifice
on my part

16:05.367 --> 16:07.800
had, honestly, not
occurred to me at all.

16:07.800 --> 16:10.133
At many points in this review

16:10.133 --> 16:13.200
I felt nostalgic for the day
when all I had to worry about

16:13.200 --> 16:15.600
was being shot in the heart
with an arrow.

16:15.600 --> 16:18.833
The power of wish is
a heavy burden

16:18.833 --> 16:21.100
that no man
should have to bear.

16:21.100 --> 16:22.833
Making someone's wish
come true,

16:22.833 --> 16:26.133
half a star.

16:30.400 --> 16:34.067
