16:34.067 --> 16:36.167
The next review
comes from Elliot

16:36.167 --> 16:38.333
in Homa Hills, Wyoming.

16:38.333 --> 16:40.067
Homa Hills.

16:40.067 --> 16:43.400
Hey, Forrest, what's it like
to be alone in a rowboat?

16:43.400 --> 16:46.433
- Hey, man--
