17:45.500 --> 17:49.467
(Forrest voice-over)
But perhaps I had allowed myself
to feel too peaceful.

17:49.467 --> 17:52.967
[snores]

17:52.967 --> 17:55.967
[dramatic music]

17:55.967 --> 17:59.900
*

